  "instructions": [
    "Press the tofu for 30 minutes to remove excess moisture.",
    "Cut the tofu into 2 cm cubes and thread them onto skewers.",
    "Whisk chickpea flour, water, a pinch of salt, and pepper into a smooth batter.",
    "Coat each tofu cube in the batter and let excess drip off.",
    "Heat sesame oil in a deep pan to 180 degrees Celsius and fry the skewers until golden brown, about 2 minutes per side.",
    "Drain the fried tofu on paper towels and serve hot.",
    "Whisk tamari, rice vinegar, grated ginger, minced garlic, and a pinch of chili flakes into a sauce.",
    "Drizzle the sauce over the tofu and sprinkle with capers before serving."
